@startuml
actor User as Actor
participant NotificationDropdown
participant NotificationController
participant NotificationDAO
participant Database

User as Actor -> NotificationDropdown : View Notifications
NotificationDropdown -> NotificationController : fetchNotifications()
NotificationController -> NotificationDAO : getNotificationsByRecipient(userId, options)
NotificationDAO -> Database : Query notifications
Database --> NotificationDAO : Return notifications
NotificationDAO --> NotificationController : Notifications data
NotificationController --> NotificationDropdown : Notifications data

User as Actor -> NotificationDropdown : Mark a notification as read
NotificationDropdown -> NotificationController : markNotificationAsRead(notificationId)
NotificationController -> NotificationDAO : markNotificationAsRead(notificationId)
NotificationDAO -> Database : Update notification
Database --> NotificationDAO : Update result
NotificationDAO --> NotificationController : Updated notification
NotificationController --> NotificationDropdown : Update confirmation

User as Actor -> NotificationDropdown : Mark all as read
NotificationDropdown -> NotificationController : markAllNotificationsAsRead(userId)
NotificationController -> NotificationDAO : markAllNotificationsAsRead(userId)
NotificationDAO -> Database : Update all unread notifications
Database --> NotificationDAO : Update result
NotificationDAO --> NotificationController : Update confirmation
NotificationController --> NotificationDropdown : Success message
@enduml
